# {{ .ProviderName }}

A Crossplane provider for managing cloud resources.

## Getting Started

### Install Provider

Apply the provider to your Crossplane cluster:

```bash
kubectl apply -f package/provider.yaml
```

### Configure Provider

Create a ProviderConfig:

```yaml
apiVersion: pkg.crossplane.io/v1
kind: Provider
metadata:
  name: {{ .ProviderName }}
spec:
  package: {{ .Repo }}
```

## Development

### Build

Run `make` to build the provider:

```bash
make
```

### Test

Run tests with:

```bash
make test
```

### Deploy

Build and deploy the provider:

```bash
make build
make deploy
```